{"ID":"20260305082130-ne5o6sm","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ne5o6sm","title":"多态与虚函数","type":"doc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082201-fhg8tk3","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082201-fhg8tk3"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eWFtbA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"---\ntitle: 多态与虚函数\ndate created: 星期一, 十月 20日 2025, 10:57:40 上午\ndate modified: 星期二, 十月 21日 2025, 1:35:53 下午\n---"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-72uoe16","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-72uoe16","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多态与虚函数"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-9ylzcpw","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-9ylzcpw","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"block-ref","TextMarkBlockRefID":"20260305082130-4fzlo5t","TextMarkBlockRefSubtype":"d","TextMarkTextContent":"多态"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" (Polymorphism)"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-e7qjc26","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-e7qjc26","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"定义："},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多态（Polymorphism）这个词来源于希腊语，意为“多种形态”。在面向对象编程 (OOP) 中，多态指的是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"允许一个接口有多种实现"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，或者说"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"允许一个对象在不同的上下文中表现出不同的行为"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"简单来说，就是“同一个操作作用于不同的对象，可以有不同的解释和行为”。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-2dvxcva","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-2dvxcva","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"C++ 中的多态类型："},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"1. 编译时多态 (Compile-time Polymorphism) / 静态多态："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-cgz4a1e","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-cgz4a1e","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-1ocfvjg","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-1ocfvjg","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-vtnvv4t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-vtnvv4t","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"实现方式："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 主要通过"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"函数重载 (Function Overloading)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"函数模板 (Function Templates)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 实现。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-8m3vfnk","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-8m3vfnk","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-60v7609","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-60v7609","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"特点："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 编译器在编译阶段就能确定调用哪个函数版本。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-crmgu4x","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-crmgu4x","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-exkins5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-exkins5","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例："}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-4rc6fkq","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-4rc6fkq","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"void print(int i) { std::cout \u003c\u003c \"Int: \" \u003c\u003c i \u003c\u003c std::endl; }\nvoid print(double d) { std::cout \u003c\u003c \"Double: \" \u003c\u003c d \u003c\u003c std::endl; }\n// print(5) 和 print(5.0) 在编译时就确定了调用哪个版本\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-cg6ux2r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-cg6ux2r","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"2. 运行时多态 (Runtime Polymorphism) / 动态多态："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-r05j2xb","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-r05j2xb","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-qccgsxd","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-qccgsxd","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-9q0966n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-9q0966n","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"实现方式："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 主要通过"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"虚函数 (Virtual Functions)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"继承 (Inheritance)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 实现。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-o4wavte","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-o4wavte","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-ylr5l2n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ylr5l2n","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"特点："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 编译器在编译阶段无法确定调用哪个函数版本，而是在"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"程序运行时"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"根据对象的实际类型来决定。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-z3qwfup","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-z3qwfup","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-dl2oe86","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-dl2oe86","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 这就是虚函数发挥作用的地方。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-nk845pw","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-nk845pw","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"block-ref","TextMarkBlockRefID":"20260305082130-gf29u2c","TextMarkBlockRefSubtype":"d","TextMarkTextContent":"虚函数"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" (Virtual Function)"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-y70jpcl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-y70jpcl","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"定义："},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虚函数是在 C++ 的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"基类 (Base Class)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 中声明的，用 ⁠virtual 关键字修饰的成员函数。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-j5zfpcf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-j5zfpcf","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"虚函数在多态中的作用："},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虚函数是 C++ 实现"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"运行时多态"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的核心机制。它允许你通过"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"基类指针或引用"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"调用派生类中重写的函数版本。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-feid8gb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-feid8gb","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"工作原理："},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当一个基类指针或引用指向一个派生类对象时，如果通过这个指针或引用调用一个虚函数，C++ 会在"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"运行时"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"检查指针或引用实际指向的对象的类型，并调用该实际类型中对应的虚函数版本。"}]}]}